Ten articles in a 1980s computer magazine by sci-fi author Ted Chiang
text:
Searching the Internet Archive, I found lots of articles by sci-fi author Ted Chiang in back issues of an old computer magazine from the late eighties from when he was studying computer science at Brown University. The magazine was called ProFiles: The Magazine for Kaypro Users.

https://archive.org/details/PROFILES_Volume_3_Number_3_1985-10_Kaypro_Corp_US/page/32
